features: 【Durable & Vintage Messenger Bag】Presented in supple textured PU leather with cowhide pattern, offers the water-proof & scratch-resistant advantage, trimmed with contrasting antique bronze hardware that conveys a classic chic fashion look and feels.

【Plenty Room for Organizing】Laptop messenger bag designed with one separate laptop compartment holds 15-15.6 Inch laptop, one big compartment for documents; The inside consist of a couple of different dividers, The front compartment has a zipper pocket that can fit about an iPad and other useful stuff easily.

【Removable & adjustable Strap】Messenger bag has an adjustable strap with shoulder pad for comfortable carry, the leather messenger bag can be used as a briefcase. Single shoulder, cross body. You can also remove the shoulder strap and carry it with the convenient handles.

【Convenient Magnetic Snap & Comfortable Fit】Laptop messenger bag is double secured by magnetic snaps and zippers. Inner padded laptop sleeve fits most laptops up to 15.6" and cohesive seal ensures it to be steady.

【Designed for Everyone】The external dimension of this briefcase is 16.1"L * 5.1"W * 12.6"H. Laptop sleeve dimension: 15.0"L * 9.5"W.It is a messenger bag which is good for school, college, business, work, travel, overnight, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The perfect old school business breifcase!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I’ve been on the hunt for the perfect, old school professional business briefcase. This is it! I just got it today so, I can’t comment on long term quality yet but, on first impressions, it’s really great quality! It feels like real leather. It’s very structured, which I love and It has 4 metal things (sorry, I’m drawing a blank on the antual name of these right now) that make the bag stand up nicely. All of the hardware feels nice and has a good weight to it. The magnetic closures work perfectly and the zippers are buttery smooth. It has lots of space and added zipper pockets on both sides. I love that it also comes with a shoulder strap although, I’ll just be carrying this by the top handle. The shoulder strap has a nice shoulder pad as well.I went with the “coffee” brown color, when I would usually choose black and I’m glad I did. The shade is beautiful! It isn’t a solid color which just adds to it. It fits everything I need and I couldn’t be more happy with this purchase!I’ll update this review if anything changes over time…

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Bang for the buck.
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to give myself a slightly more professional look at work over the backpack that I previously used, this bag does exactly that and the price was right. I've already received several compliments on it in just a couple of weeks. It has many pockets which is nice. Time will tell if the bag will stand the rest of time, which it may or may not but at the price point if I get a couple of good years out of it I'll be very happy and anything beyond that will be a bonus.

reviews.reviewText: Just got this briefcase today. Specifies that it’s for men but as a woman I loved it when I saw it so I bought it for myself. That being said, I do love the look, and it fits everything that I need in it.
